00:00:12.249 --> 00:00:17.740
Clinical mass hysteria describes the spread
of a psychologically-manifested illness. One

00:00:17.740 --> 00:00:23.529
or two people show signs of illness that they
blame on poison gas, genies or a ghost, and

00:00:23.529 --> 00:00:29.519
suddenly others begin to show the same symptoms
-- or worse. Mass hysteria typically occurs

00:00:29.519 --> 00:00:35.940
in high-stress situations among people in
confined areas like schools, factories or

00:00:35.940 --> 00:00:38.039
small villages in Colonial Massachusetts.

